{
  "texts": [
    "Many students are still surprised to learn that AI can make up things that may not be true while sounding highly convincing. 5.",
    "Some of the students having a clear understanding of the hallucinatory AI problems still feel ill equipped to deal with them.",
    "As such, KFH has the intent to help its students to learn to deal with AI in a responsible fashion.",
    "For the members of the AI-Taskforce and the university's leadership, this has come to mean that the use of ChatGPT and other LLMs are neither prohibited nor allowed without restrictions.",
    "Just exactly how such a framework would look like and could be implemented was subject to intense debate."
  ]
}